{"title":"Rhodoks的lca","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":512,"tags":["2020小学期"],"operation":{"submit":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1179#submit_code","submissions":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/submissions?problem_id=1179","statistics":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1179/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1179/testdata","discussion":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/discussion/problem/1179"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"$\\text{Rhodoks}$很喜欢$lca$，所以他给了你一棵$n$个结点的树，要你求出：\r\n\r\n$$\\sum_{i=1}^{n} \\sum_{j=1}^{n} i \\times j \\times lca(i,j)$$\r\n\r\n上式中$lca(i,j)$指$i$和$j$最近公共祖先的编号。所谓最近公共祖先，是指满足既是$i$的祖先也是$j$的祖先的深度最大的那个节点。我们认为节点自身也是自己的祖先。\r\n\r\n树的结点从$1-n$编号，根节点为$1$号节点，答案对$998244353$取模。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输入数据第一行仅一个正整数$n$，含义如上所述。\r\n\r\n接下来$n-1$行，每行两个正整数$x,y$代表从$x$到$y$连接有一条边。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"仅一个正整数，为答案。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"#### 样例输入\r\n```plain\r\n5\r\n1 2\r\n1 3\r\n2 4\r\n2 5\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出\r\n```plain\r\n471\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"$1 \\leq n \\leq 3 \\times 10^5$\r\n\r\n$1 \\leq x,y \\leq n$"}]}